Sentencas: Micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell (SOFC) modules consisting of 1 mm thick, 1.2 cm wide micro flat-tube SOFCs, gas manifold, and insulator have been fabricated and evaluated using simple gas heating apparatus.
Titulo: Evaluation of micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell modules using simple gas heating apparatus

Sentencas: The cell consists of NiO - yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) as an anode (flat-tube support), scandia stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) as an electrolyte, gadolinia doped ceria (GDC) for an interlayer, and (La, Sr)(Fe, Co)O-3 (LSCF)
Titulo: Evaluation of micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell modules using simple gas heating apparatus

Sentencas: - GDC as a cathode, which has been fabricated using cost effective extrusion technique and dip-coating technique.
Titulo: Evaluation of micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell modules using simple gas heating apparatus

Sentencas: The cell has been investigated between 600 and 650 degrees C operating temperature and showed the power density at 0.75 V of 0.19 and 0385 W cm(-2), respectively.
Titulo: Evaluation of micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell modules using simple gas heating apparatus

Sentencas: Using the cell, a five and ten-series modules were assembled and stored in insulator with small gas heaters powered by a 24 V power source for start-up.
Titulo: Evaluation of micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell modules using simple gas heating apparatus

Sentencas: The module successfully operated using hydrogen and methane fuel.
Titulo: Evaluation of micro flat-tube solid-oxide fuel cell modules using simple gas heating apparatus
